    "body" : "<p>VS Code IntelliSense features are powered by a language service, and there's AI-assisted IntelliSense called <a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=VisualStudioExptTeam.vscodeintellicode\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Visual Studio IntelliCode</a> which you can install from extension marketplace. When you find IntelliSense has stopped working, the language service may not be running. Try reinstalling the <code>java extension pack</code> and restarting VS Code and this should solve the issue.</p>\n"
